{"tid":2348564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上年元旦，有無數人被捕","createTime":"2020-12-31T19:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:07:31.000Z","uid":6845,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"823b173a1fa5948366113d13a0b32779de49da97","tid":2348564,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"上年元旦，有無數人被捕，一大堆人判社服,感化,守行為（sorry太多無法列出）亦有一堆人監禁式刑罰（而家仲有一大堆人未完案）：<br />\n<br />\n#20200101紅磡 紅隧POOW拒捕違武 37歲廖判八個月（610）被狗圍毆拳打腳踼，上庭下巴有膠布，離庭大嗌「唔洗擔心！我自己會頂住！」得幾人送車<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F5879&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=3fb569a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5879</a><br />\n<br />\n#20200101灣仔 POOW有意POOW 大學講師37歲岑判一年（827）得幾人送車<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8766&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=116b69c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8766</a><br />\n<br />\n#20200101銅鑼灣 POOW 24歲劉判九個月（94）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9091&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a93d1f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9091</a><br />\n<br />\n#20200101旺角 襲狗22歲李25歲利判三個月（918）同案無辜還押約90日，被狗圍毆<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9590&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=7242011d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9590</a><br />\n<br />\n想提及一下嘅手足<br />\n#20200101灣仔 新工會街站鐵蓮花19歲任被捕至少兩次 無辜還押兩個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8486&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c0b3f99a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8486</a><br />\n<br />\n#20200101灣仔 裝修中銀3個手足受傷仲要被黃屍割係鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12030&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=6224f246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12030</a>"},{"pid":"8b03dd855f0d69b70bb152a5b4344b0fbfe49013","tid":2348564,"uid":238973,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADGxfss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADGxfss.jpg&h=c32ea9ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed9750e08fd429650697d590436b1f5ebf11042d","tid":2348564,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8b03dd855f0d69b70bb152a5b4344b0fbfe49013","tid":2348564,"uid":238973,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADGxfss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADGxfss.jpg&h=c32ea9ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662c067b3c5255eefc4cb1b641880b8f86e05535","tid":2348564,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:36:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9b5c66c14e34c337d353ed31105d8b6230ef1bb","tid":2348564,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:42:48.000Z","msg":"記得嗎 等佢嗎"},{"pid":"8036df7bcd288a41bd3216eeca66c98a72dc853f","tid":2348564,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:4